<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8" standalone="no"?><?Xpress productLine="ncc-clause" ?><clause id="_11be0cd2-555f-4b07-9191-40c0c8a07c30" outputclass="ncc-clause"><meta><facet building="Class 1a"/><facet building="Class 1b"/><facet building="Class 10a"/><facet building="Class 10b"/><facet building="Class 10c"/></meta><sptc>S30C3</sptc><title id="_82c52931-b282-4520-884b-2abd8abcc30b">Floors and drainage</title><archive-num>2019: Spec G2.2: 2.2</archive-num><subclause id="_a6b2d024-291e-4776-8408-47a0dda0491e" outputclass="subclause"><title id="_b20c1034-7f1f-4ef7-9e45-3de6964907a8">SubClause</title><num>1</num><p>Floor surfaces beneath <xref format="dita" href="/tmp/QppServer/Publishing/5e2c1f63-e589-4ce1-95e8-5c3e286a7aff/1210_0.10.0.xml#_5e4c02dd-0737-47ed-ad7b-5de888c05ed7" id="_16fb2fcc-24d8-4516-98af-c0bc4a950495" scope="local" type="abcb-glossentry">boilers</xref> and <xref format="dita" href="/tmp/QppServer/Publishing/5e2c1f63-e589-4ce1-95e8-5c3e286a7aff/1405_5.1.0.xml#_3be0ceb4-ef72-40e5-8aaa-ae75f63e4bd4" id="_5e7ef074-27f5-4c88-ad34-b72906c1dda5" scope="local" type="abcb-glossentry">pressure vessels</xref> shall be <xref format="dita" href="/tmp/QppServer/Publishing/5e2c1f63-e589-4ce1-95e8-5c3e286a7aff/1520_0.5.0.xml#_787642fb-810b-4dc9-8ea9-f54fcfbc19e1" id="_6b5ab811-36c9-49d5-9add-c8d5e275b646" scope="local" type="abcb-glossentry">water resistant</xref> and formed to drain away from supports and structural building elements.</p></subclause><subclause id="_235d1e8c-5869-47f4-968d-2dd04be082d8" outputclass="subclause"><title id="_9196dbe5-643c-4a4a-9350-54754fc1e54a">SubClause</title><num>2</num><p>Where a safe tray is provided to trap liquids, it must be manufactured from a material resistant to corrosion from the contents of the <xref format="dita" href="/tmp/QppServer/Publishing/5e2c1f63-e589-4ce1-95e8-5c3e286a7aff/1210_0.10.0.xml#_5e4c02dd-0737-47ed-ad7b-5de888c05ed7" id="_bc5128fc-9782-417a-8236-97402e1517a3" scope="local" type="abcb-glossentry">boiler</xref> or <xref format="dita" href="/tmp/QppServer/Publishing/5e2c1f63-e589-4ce1-95e8-5c3e286a7aff/1405_5.1.0.xml#_3be0ceb4-ef72-40e5-8aaa-ae75f63e4bd4" id="_00c3058a-4008-4147-b868-b207179d896d" scope="local" type="abcb-glossentry">pressure vessel</xref>.</p></subclause></clause>